
Upload function
------------------

To use the upload function you need to create a folder C:/MCPackage on your disk
(it's usually not necessary to set a path, it's created automatically) 
or change the path in the Class de.tudresden.gis.manage.xml.Constants


Review/Comment function
--------------------------

To use the review/comment function you need to create a folder C:/MCComments on your disk
or change the path in the File \\geoportal\WEB-INF\classes\gpt\config\gpt.xml

https://github.com/Esri/geoportal-server/wiki/Ratings-and-Comments-for-Search-Results


Modify Search Criteria
--------------------------

https://github.com/Esri/geoportal-server/wiki/Add-Custom-Search-Criteria


Use new Schema (MCP)
--------------------------

https://github.com/Esri/geoportal-server/wiki/Add-a-Custom-Profile


Browse Tree anpassen
--------------------------

https://github.com/Esri/geoportal-server/wiki/Browse-Tree


Admin Add Old Metadata Editors
--------------------------------

Add to addMetadataBody.jsp:
<f:selectItem itemValue="register" itemLabel="#{gptMsg['catalog.publication.addMetadata.command.register']}"/>
<f:selectItem itemValue="edit" itemLabel="#{gptMsg['catalog.publication.addMetadata.command.edit']}"/>
    
